\ Compile font shapes into VDP at compile time
\ This method consumes NO program space but is slow

\ ARIAL style font (SANS Serif)
DECIMAL
\ tool to see your font
: .FONT  CR  128 30 DO  I EMIT LOOP  ;

NEEDS MARKER FROM DSK1.MARKER

MARKER REMOVE

\ this library gives us simple memory managment for VDP
\ the works like the Forth dictionary
NEEDS V,  FROM DSK1.VDPMEM

HEX
: ]PDT  ( n -- vaddr) 8* 800 + ;

1E ]PDT  VP !   \ set VDP memory pointer to character 1E location

